profile_summary: Detail-oriented and highly organized Warehouse Assistant with a strong background in logistics and inventory management. Proven ability to manage warehouse operations, maintain accurate inventory records, and ensure timely dispatch and receipt of goods. Currently working as an Airbnb Supervisor, demonstrating exceptional customer service skills and the ability to manage multiple tasks simultaneously. Committed to maintaining a safe and efficient warehouse environment.

description: Managing the day-to-day operations of the Airbnb property
Ensuring the property is clean and well-maintained for guests
Handling guest inquiries and resolving any issues promptly
Coordinating with service providers for property maintenance
Maintaining high standards of customer service
Ensured timely dispatch and receipt of goods
Complied with safety regulations and procedures
Assisted in loading and unloading goods
Worked effectively as part of a team to meet targets
achievements: Improved inventory accuracy by 20% through meticulous record-keeping
